### **Test 1: Admin Login**
```
POST http://localhost:8081/admins/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "admin1",
  "password": "admin123"
}

Expected Response: "OK"
```

### **Test 2: Get All Users (No Token Required)**
```
GET http://localhost:8081/users/all

Expected Response: User list (no 403 error)
```

### **Test 3: Activate User + Email**
```
PUT http://localhost:8081/users/1/activate

Expected Response: "USER ACTIVATED, MAIL SENT"
Expected: Email sent to user
```

### **Test 4: Frontend**
```
